base_token_id.desc: The main lending token used for deposits and borrowing (0 for ALGO)

lst_token_id.desc: LST (Liquidity Staking Token) representing depositor shares in the pool

circulating_lst.desc: Total LST tokens currently in circulation (represents depositor claims)

total_deposits.desc: Total underlying assets deposited in the protocol

admin_account.desc: Administrative account with privileged access to protocol functions

oracle_app.desc: External oracle application for asset price feeds

flux_oracle_app.desc: External oracle application for user flux tier feeds

ltv_bps.desc: Loan-to-Value ratio (e.g., 7500 = 75% max borrowing against collateral)

liq_threshold_bps.desc: Liquidation threshold (e.g., 8500 = 85% - liquidate when CR falls below)

origination_fee_bps.desc: One-time fee charged on loan origination (e.g., 100 = 1%)

base_bps.desc: Minimum APR at 0% utilization (basis points per year).

util_cap_bps.desc: Hard utilization cap in bps (e.g., 8000 = 80% of deposits may be borrowed).

kink_norm_bps.desc: Kink point on normalized utilization (0..10_000 across [0..util_cap]).

slope1_bps.desc: APR increase from 0 → kink (added to base) over the normalized range.

slope2_bps.desc: APR increase from kink → cap (added after kink) over the normalized range.

max_apr_bps.desc: (Optional) Absolute APR ceiling in bps (0 = no cap).

prev_apr_bps.desc: (Optional, mutable) Last applied APR in bps (for step limiting).

total_borrows.desc: Total outstanding borrower principal + accrued interest (debt)

borrow_index_wad.desc: Multiplicative borrow index (scaled by INDEX_SCALE). Starts at INDEX_SCALE

last_accrual_ts.desc: Timestamp (ledger seconds) at which borrow_index_wad was last advanced

last_apr_bps.desc: APR (in bps) that applied during [last_accrual_ts, now) before recompute

total_borrows_principal.desc: Sum of borrower principals (no interest). We’ll migrate total_borrows usage.

active_loan_records.desc: Total number of active loans in the system

accepted_collaterals_count.desc: Count of different collateral types accepted by the protocol

buyout_token_id.desc: Total number of active loans in the system

liq_bonus_bps.desc: Liquidation bonus in bps (e.g., 500 = 5% bonus to liquidators)

accepted_collaterals.desc: Registry of accepted collateral assets with their metadata

loan_record.desc: Individual borrower loan records with collateral and debt details
